# Docker Build Exclusion List
# ===========================
# Mirrors .deployignore — the canonical exclusion list for this project.
# Docker respects this file natively during COPY and build context assembly.
# If you update exclusions, update .deployignore as well to keep them in sync.

# AI development framework
.claude/

# GitHub configuration
.github/

# Git and deployment meta files
.git/
.gitignore
.deployignore
.dockerignore

# Template and project documentation
README.md
INIT_INSTRUCTIONS.md
LICENSE

# Legacy and reference directories
CLAUDE_AI_INIT_PROJECT/
references/

# IDE and editor files
.vscode/
.idea/
*.swp
*.swo
*~

# Project-specific exclusions
# Add lines below for files that exist in the repo but should not be in the image.
# Examples:
#   tests/
#   docs/
#   Makefile
#   *.md
